Name: OctoFX
Description: This is a sample application with a SQL Server database, an ASP.NET MVC frontend, and a Windows Service that runs in the background. The app is deployed live; you can find it at: - Dev: [dev.octofx.com](http://dev.octofx.com) - Test: [test.octofx.com](http://dev.octofx.com) - Production: [octofx.com](http://dev.octofx.com) Source code for the app is on GitHub: [OctopusSamples/OctoFX](https://github.com/OctopusSamples/OctoFX) The project uses TeamCity as the build server - you can log in to TeamCity as a guest: [TeamCity Build Server](http://teamcity.octopusdeploy.com)
